<p>For every three points of damage dealt to a Goblin in a single blow, one is considered a Deep Wound. Goblins receive Synergy Class bonuses at a rate of one for every six levels gained.</p>

<h2>Dwarves</h2>

<p>Dwarf stats are chosen in the same way as Wolf stats are chosen. For every four points of damage dealt to a Dwarf in a single blow, one is considered a Deep Wound.</p>

<h2>Vampires</h2>

<p>Vampires have <%= str %>, <%= dex %> and <%= int %> of d12 and <%= fai %> of 4. Poison damage only does regular wounds to Vampires. However fire damage deal Deep Wounds. Vampires reduce any penalty to darkness by two but penalties due to light, if any, are increased by one. Vampires must have the abilities <%= skill 'Atheist' %> and <%= skill 'Literate' %>.</p>